{{Top|leg}}
The '''Rull''' was a [[thildas]], or clan, of [[Ebranite]]s. Even during the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] era, when most of the Ebranite clans had learned to co-operate with one another, the Rull continued their feuding ways. Another clan with a similar outlook was the [[Jih-tan]], who may have been their rivals.

The symbol of the Rulls, which was tattooed on the upper left arm of each of its members, was a flaming [[hag'thyyr]] holding a spear.

Notable members of this thildas include [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] operatives [[Rith Tar'ak]], [[Tor'ara]] and [[Nyik]].

